From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:31:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve TypeScript errors, remove tracked dist/, clean
 up project

- Add vite-env.d.ts for Vite environment type declarations
- Fix AccessLogsModal async bug (setLogs receiving Promise instead of value)
- Fix geminiService.proxy.ts type mismatches (SearchResult, ComparisonResult)
- Fix simplesNacionalService.ts Firestore null reference in closure
- Update .env.example with all Firebase config variables
- Remove feature branch trigger from deploy.yml (main only)
- Remove duplicate src/server.js (proxy-backend/server.js is canonical)
- Remove credentials_json placeholder file
- Add dist/, credentials_json to .gitignore
- Remove dist/ from git tracking (built during CI/CD)

